| Test Case ID | Feature             | Test Scenario                                             | Test Steps                                                                                                     | Expected Result                                                         | Status |
| ------------ | ------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------ |
| TC_01        | Image Upload        | Check if user can upload a handwritten digit image        | 1. Open system 2. Click upload button 3. Select digit image 4. Submit                                          | Image should upload successfully                                        | Pass   |
| TC_02        | Image Preprocessing | Check if uploaded image is converted into required format | 1. Upload digit image 2. System resizes image 3. System converts image to grayscale 4. System normalizes image | Image should convert into model-ready format                            | Pass   |
| TC_03        | Digit Prediction    | Check if model predicts correct digit                     | 1. Upload image of digit `7` 2. Click predict button 3. View output                                            | System should show predicted digit `7`                                  | Pass   |
| TC_04        | Confidence Score    | Check if prediction confidence is displayed               | 1. Upload valid digit image 2. Run prediction 3. Check result area                                             | System should display confidence score, e.g. `95%`                      | Pass   |
| TC_05        | Prediction History  | Check if prediction record is saved using Pandas/CSV      | 1. Upload image 2. Predict digit 3. Open prediction history table/CSV                                          | Record should include image name, predicted digit, confidence, and date | Pass   |
